article_title: Declining Unemployment, Strong Job Additions To Drive Revenues

article_metadata.author: Great Speculations

og.description: We expect to see an increase in Paychex’s checks per client driven by the decline in the unemployment rate to a six-year low. Also, as the deadline for compliance with the Affordable Care Act regulation approaches, Paychex should see an increase in its client base.
